
    MADALA Mbuso Mkhize (73) has dreamt of living in a decent house his whole life.When President Jacob Zuma visited the area during his campaign in 2013, he promised the madala a decent home. But four years later, the madala is still living in a mud house at Snathing, Pietermaritzburg, in the KZN Midlands.Madala Mbuso, who needs a wheelchair to move around, has realised that the president was just campaigning.“He witnessed the conditions I live in. He promised he would build a house for me. He came with a councillor and gave the councillor the task of finding suitable land to build me a proper home.“I have no legs and one arm and I survive on a government grant. I am so sad that the councillor never got back to me.”Councillor Sipho Madonda confirmed that the president had visited Mkhize.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsvN7uscoERfrJZLJ1zA2vyvB6WHjY7QL7XInnj9dc3DSxO4HF6fyAxeCjYRZRNo0UOZC8zPnTpoJ_IaeUlkarnWyuGsymSQbjizifOSmrBR1scbKJn1ZWipuer_MZ6tIhrnexerl3SlJIEp0vnR-0dxJaHBhi1IvRiNOhGcC1l5Tg3du6eu-wqj-vZZuSHZpKeZAKcD2v9pBYVi8eQJsbC_r-cPwtiVmYwNhqyUywgnoSQj4U8IViea8kOxBbAnasufdJrQl83ohfKxkwKMK10P0FGxveY\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzDgiBLqkZbDuEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
